### Mutlimodal-Interaction

#### Installation
Follow these steps in order to install the project
```
git config --global user.name "Surname Name"
git config --global user.email "Mail address"
git clone https://github.com/thibautquentinjacob/Mutlimodal-Interaction.git
git remote add upstream https://github.com/thibautquentinjacob/Mutlimodal-Interaction.git
git fetch upstream
...
git commit -a -m "committing changes"
git push
```
